{"title":"JupyterNotebook","uid":"886a5f0c89c241749d15d620f409205c","slug":"JupyterNotebook","date":"2022-03-22T08:26:26.000Z","updated":"2022-03-31T06:11:35.322Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/JupyterNotebook.json","keywords":"Blog","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/jupyterbackground.jpg"],"content":"<p>Jupyter Notebook是基于网页的用于交互计算的应用程序。其可被应用于全过程计算：开发、文档编写、运行代码和展示结果。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n\n<h1 id=\"1-简介\"><a href=\"#1-简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 简介\"></a><strong>1. 简介</strong></h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Jupyter Notebook是基于网页的用于交互计算的应用程序。其可被应用于全过程计算：开发、文档编写、运行代码和展示结果。——<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https://jupyter-notebook.readthedocs.io/en/stable/notebook.html\">Jupyter Notebook官方介绍</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>简而言之，Jupyter Notebook是以网页的形式打开，可以在网页页面中<strong>直接编写代码</strong>和<strong>运行代码</strong>，代码的<strong>运行结果</strong>也会直接在代码块下显示的程序。如在编程过程中需要编写说明文档，可在同一个页面中直接编写，便于作及时的说明和解释。</p>\n<h1 id=\"2-组成部分\"><a href=\"#2-组成部分\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 组成部分\"></a><strong>2. 组成部分</strong></h1><h2 id=\"①-网页应用\"><a href=\"#①-网页应用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"① 网页应用\"></a><strong>① 网页应用</strong></h2><p>网页应用即基于网页形式的、结合了编写说明文档、数学公式、交互计算和其他富媒体形式的工具。<strong>简言之，网页应用是可以实现各种功能的工具。</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"②-文档\"><a href=\"#②-文档\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"② 文档\"></a><strong>② 文档</strong></h2><p>即Jupyter Notebook中所有交互计算、编写说明文档、数学公式、图片以及其他富媒体形式的输入和输出，都是以文档的形式体现的。</p>\n<p>这些文档是保存为后缀名为<code>.ipynb</code>的<code>JSON</code>格式文件，不仅便于版本控制，也方便与他人共享。</p>\n<p>此外，文档还可以导出为：HTML、LaTeX、PDF等格式。</p>\n<h1 id=\"3-Jupyter-Notebook的主要特点\"><a href=\"#3-Jupyter-Notebook的主要特点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. Jupyter Notebook的主要特点\"></a><strong>3. Jupyter Notebook的主要特点</strong></h1><p>① 编程时具有<strong>语法高亮</strong>、<em>缩进</em>、<em>tab补全</em>的功能。</p>\n<p>② 可直接通过浏览器运行代码，同时在代码块下方展示运行结果。</p>\n<p>③ 以富媒体格式展示计算结果。富媒体格式包括：HTML，LaTeX，PNG，SVG等。</p>\n<p>④ 对代码编写说明文档或语句时，支持Markdown语法。</p>\n<p>⑤ 支持使用LaTeX编写数学性说明。</p>\n<h1 id=\"参考资料\"><a href=\"#参考资料\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考资料\"></a>参考资料</h1><p><a href=\"https://jupyter.org/\">Project Jupyter | Home</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://jupyter-notebook.readthedocs.io/en/stable/notebook.html\">The Jupyter Notebook — Jupyter Notebook 6.4.10 documentation (jupyter-notebook.readthedocs.io)</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/33105153\">Jupyter Notebook介绍、安装及使用教程 - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a></p>\n","feature":false,"text":"Jupyter Notebook是基于网页的用于交互计算的应...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":853,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"工具利器","slug":"工具利器","count":7,"path":"api/categories/工具利器.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":8,"path":"api/tags/Python.json"},{"name":"深度学习","slug":"深度学习","count":4,"path":"api/tags/深度学习.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. 简介</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. 组成部分</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E2%91%A0-%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">① 网页应用</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E2%91%A1-%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">② 文档</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-Jupyter-Notebook%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3. Jupyter Notebook的主要特点</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">参考资料</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"https://stackoverflow.com/users/18627097/murphy","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/CosmicDusty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/294812632"}}}},"map